OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777810266
OL,3,CTribute to 'brave, deeply loyal'
OL,4,Cteenage motorcyclist who died in crash
OL,6,FThe family of a teenage motorcyclist
OL,7,Fwho died in a crash in Southampton
OL,8,Fhave described him as "brave" and
OL,9,F"deeply loyal".
OL,11,FZain Shaw, who was 17 and from
OL,12,FFareham, died following the incident
OL,13,Fon Northam Bridge on April 25 2026,
OL,14,Fwhich involved a silver Volkswagen
OL,15,FPolo and a black Yamaha YZF motorbike.
OL,17,FIn a statement, his family said: "Zain
OL,18,Fwas a brave, funny and deeply loyal
OL,19,Fyoung man who brought light and
OL,20,Flaughter into our lives.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777810266
OL,3,CTribute to 'brave, deeply loyal'
OL,4,Cteenage motorcyclist who died in crash
OL,6,F"He was loved by his family and
OL,7,Ffriends more than words can express.
OL,8,FHis warmth, kindness and spirit will
OL,9,Fremain with us always.
OL,11,F"Our hearts are broken but we take
OL,12,Fcomfort in the memories we shared and
OL,13,Fthe joy he gave us in his 17 years.
OL,15,F"Zain loved riding his motorbike, and
OL,16,Fwe take comfort in knowing he was out
OL,17,Fdoing something he loved."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777810266
OL,3,CTribute to 'brave, deeply loyal'
OL,4,Cteenage motorcyclist who died in crash
OL,6,FThey continued: "We have been
OL,7,Foverwhelmed by the support and kind
OL,8,Fmessages we've received and we are
OL,9,Ftruly grateful for everyone who has
OL,10,Freached out.
OL,12,F"We also want to thank the emergency
OL,13,Fservices for their efforts at the
OL,14,Fscene and for their compassion and
OL,15,Fsupport during this unimaginable time."
OL,17,FA 17-year-old boy and a 29-year-old
OL,18,Fman from Southampton, who were both in
OL,19,Fthe VW Polo, were arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of causing death by careless/
OL,21,Finconsiderate driving.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777810266
OL,3,CTribute to 'brave, deeply loyal'
OL,4,Cteenage motorcyclist who died in crash
OL,6,FThe 17-year-old has since been
OL,7,Freleased from custody and will face no
OL,8,Ffurther action in relation to this
OL,9,Foffence.
OL,11,FThe 29-year-old man has been released
OL,12,Fbut remains under investigation while
OL,13,FHampshire Police continue their
OL,14,Fenquiries.
OL,16,FPolice are asking anyone with
OL,17,Finformation about the collision to
OL,18,Fcontact them on 101, quoting reference
OL,19,F44260192933.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
